Package com.mycompany.ui

Class Rocket

java.lang.Object
com.mycompany.ui.MovingObject
com.mycompany.ui.Rocket
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collidable
public class Rocket
extends MovingObject
implements Collidable
This class represents a rocket within outer space aka the factory. It inherits from the MovingObject class and implements the Collidable interface. There is 1 rocket per round.
Author:
jnesis. adapted by stacey
